==制作==
===籌拍===
電影構思是來自先前瓊斯在2000年代早期閲讀了一篇關於一個網站使用人工智慧程式進行[[即時通訊|即時通訊]]的網路文章。瓊斯説：「就是第一次，也許只有20秒，它真的（在腦中）產生嗡嗡聲。」他接著説道：「我説：『嘿，你好。』而它會説：『嘿，你好嗎？』這真的令人會發出哇（……）的聲音，實在猶如產生了錯覺。在20秒之後，它快速撕裂消失。雖然你意識到這其實可以嘗試，但并非讓人如此興奮。然而，20秒時的刺激感還在。越多人談及它，它就變得更聰明。」<ref name="Guardian">{{cite web|last=Michael|first=Chris|title=Spike Jonze on letting Her rip and Being John Malkovich|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2013/sep/09/spike-jonze-her-scarlett-johansson|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|accessdate=2013-12-04|date=2013-09-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131201194852/http://www.theguardian.com/film/filmblog/2013/sep/09/spike-jonze-her-scarlett-johansson|archive-date=2013-12-01|dead-url=no}}</ref>瓊斯對於項目的興趣在執導有相同主題的短片《{{link-en|我在這兒|I'm Here (film)}}》之後重新開始<ref>{{cite web|last=Toro|first=Gabe|title=NYFF: Spike Jonze And His 'Her' Cast Decode Romance In The Age Of Technology|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/nyff-spike-jonze-and-cast-decode-romance-in-the-technology-age-in-her-20131013|publisher=Indiewire|accessdate=2013-12-04|date=2013-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131016003356/http://blogs.indiewire.com/theplaylist/nyff-spike-jonze-and-cast-decode-romance-in-the-technology-age-in-her-20131013|archive-date=2013-10-16|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。靈感還來自-{zh-hans:考夫曼; zh-hk:卡夫曼; zh-tw:考夫曼;}-在《{{link-en|紐約浮世繪|Synecdoche, New York|-{zh-hans:纽约提喻法; zh-tw:紐約浮世繪;}-}}》的寫作方式。瓊斯解釋道：「（-{zh-hans:考夫曼; zh-hk:卡夫曼; zh-tw:考夫曼;}-）説他想嘗試寫下那一刻所想的一切——當時所有的想法和感受——並把它放進劇本。我深受啓發，並試著將這種做法放進去（《雲端情人》）。同時，你對戀情和科技的許多感覺通常是矛盾的。」<ref name="Guardian" />

瓊斯花費五個月來創作劇本的首稿，他的首部電影劇本是自己獨立完成<ref>{{cite web|last=Villapaz|first=Luke|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/her-trailer-new-spike-jonze-film-featuring-joaquin-phoenix-siri-scarlett-johansson-video-1378109|title='Her' Trailer: New Spike Jonze Film Featuring Joaquin Phoenix And A Siri-Like Scarlett Johansson [VIDEO]|work=[[国际财经时报|International Business Times]]|date=2013-08-08|accessdate=2014-07-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140812193148/http://www.ibtimes.com/her-trailer-new-spike-jonze-film-featuring-joaquin-phoenix-siri-scarlett-johansson-video-1378109|archive-date=2014-08-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他為電影設想的首批演員之一是[[祖昆·馮力士|祖昆·馮力士]]<ref name="variety1">{{cite web|last=Riley|first=Jenelle|title='Her': Spike Jonze Brings His Singular Vision to the Year’s Most Offbeat Romance|url=https://variety.com/2013/film/news/her-spike-jonze-scarlett-johansson-joaquin-phoenix-1200938214/|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|accessdate=2013-12-10|date=2013-12-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131212214709/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/her-spike-jonze-scarlett-johansson-joaquin-phoenix-1200938214/|archive-date=2013-12-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年晚期，菲尼克斯加入劇組，而[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟影業]]取得分銷權<ref>{{cite web |last=Lussier |first=Germain |title=Warner Bros. Picks Up Charlie Kaufman/Spike Jonze Film; Joaquin Phoenix Attached |url=http://www.slashfilm.com/warner-bros-picks-charlie-kaufmanspike-jonze-film-joaquin-phoenix-attached/ |publisher=/Film |accessdate=2013-12-04 |date=2011-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131213193032/http://www.slashfilm.com/warner-bros-picks-charlie-kaufmanspike-jonze-film-joaquin-phoenix-attached/ |archive-date=2013-12-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[嘉莉·慕萊根|嘉莉·慕萊根]]為出演電影而進行洽談<ref>{{cite web|last=Kroll|first=Justin|title=Carey Mulligan boards pics for Coens, Spike Jonze|url=https://variety.com/2011/film/news/carey-mulligan-boards-pics-for-coens-spike-jonze-1118044810/|work=Variety|publisher=Penske Media Corporation|accessdate=2013-12-04|date=2011-10-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131218091022/http://variety.com/2011/film/news/carey-mulligan-boards-pics-for-coens-spike-jonze-1118044810/|archive-date=2013-12-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雖然-{zh-cn:她;zh-hk:她;zh-tw:她;}-決定出演，但之後因為檔期衝突問題退出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/rooney-mara-spike-jonze/|title=Rooney Mara to Replace Carey Mulligan in Spike Jonze's Untitled Project|last=Chitwood|first=Adam|publisher=Collider|date=2012-04-25|accessdate=2015-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150213181848/http://collider.com/rooney-mara-spike-jonze/|archive-date=2015-02-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2012年4月，[[魯妮·瑪拉|魯妮·瑪拉]]加入並飾演-{zh-cn:马利根; zh-hk:慕萊根; zh-tw:墨里根;}-的角色<ref>{{cite web|last=Kroll|first=Justin|title=Rooney Mara in final talks for Spike Jonze pic|url=https://variety.com/2012/film/news/rooney-mara-in-final-talks-for-spike-jonze-pic-1118053111/|work=Variety|accessdate=2013-12-04|date=2012-04-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104122745/http://variety.com/2012/film/news/rooney-mara-in-final-talks-for-spike-jonze-pic-1118053111/|archive-date=2013-11-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[克里斯·普瑞特|克里斯·普瑞特]]于2013年5月宣佈出演電影<ref>{{cite news|last1=Keong|first1=Lori|title=Scarlett Johansson, Chris Pratt Added to Spike Jonze Sci-Fi Film ''Her''|url=http://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2013/05/new-spike-jonze-sci-fi-film-her-will-star-scarlett.html|accessdate=2015-02-13|work=Paste Magazine|date=2013-05-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150213182330/http://www.pastemagazine.com/articles/2013/05/new-spike-jonze-sci-fi-film-her-will-star-scarlett.html|archive-date=2015-02-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

瓊斯長期的[[攝影指導|攝影指導]]{{tsl|en|Lance Acord|蘭斯·阿卡德}}並不能拍攝電影。因為如此，瓊斯聘請了霍伊特·範·霍特瑪<ref name=dystopian>{{cite web|last1=Tapley|first1=Kristopher|title=Cinematographer Hoyte Van Hoytema on capturing Spike Jonze's 'Her' through a non-dystopian lens|url=http://www.hitfix.com/in-contention/cinematographer-hoyte-van-hoytema-on-capturing-spike-jonzes-her-through-a-non-dystopian-lens|website=Hitflix|accessdate=2015-09-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150921045315/http://www.hitfix.com/in-contention/cinematographer-hoyte-van-hoytema-on-capturing-spike-jonzes-her-through-a-non-dystopian-lens|archive-date=2015-09-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在討論電影的外觀時，瓊斯告訴範·霍特瑪他不想要呈現[[反烏托邦|反烏托邦]]的樣子，於是兩人採用範·霍特瑪所説的「就像有點概念性和非常具備理論性的混合」風格<ref name=dystopian/>。範·霍特瑪從日本攝影師[[川内倫子|川內倫子]]獲得特別的靈感<ref name=dystopian/>。為了與電影主題保持一致，範·霍特瑪盡可能試圖避免使用藍色，讓其感覺能與科幻類型有很好的關聯<ref name=dystopian/>。他還認為通過消除顔色，它會使剩餘顔色「具有特定身份」<ref name=dystopian/>。

===拍攝===
《雲端情人》的[[主體拍攝|主體拍攝]]於2012年中期進行<ref name="SlashFilm">{{cite web|url=http://www.slashfilm.com/spike-jonzes-movie-with-joaquin-phoenix-gets-new-title-official-synopsis|title=Spike Jonze’s Movie With Joaquin Phoenix Gets New Title, Official Synopsis|last=Han|first=Angie|publisher=/Film|date=2012-08-31|accessdate=2012-08-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120902194245/http://www.slashfilm.com/spike-jonzes-movie-with-joaquin-phoenix-gets-new-title-official-synopsis/|archive-date=2012-09-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>，製片預算是2,300萬美元<ref name="mojo" />。它主要在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]拍攝，并由額外的兩周是在[[上海市|上海]]拍攝<ref name="vulture">{{cite web|last=Harris|first=Mark|title=Him and Her: How Spike Jonze Made the Weirdest, Most Timely Romance of the Year|url=http://www.vulture.com/2013/10/spike-jonze-on-making-her.html|work=New York|accessdate=2013-12-05|date=2013-10-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131206085722/http://www.vulture.com/2013/10/spike-jonze-on-making-her.html|archive-date=2013-12-06|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在製作電影的過程中，女演員{{le|薩曼莎·莫頓|Samantha Morton}}飾演莎曼珊的角色，-{zh-cn:她;zh-hk:她;zh-tw:她;}-在「黑色彩繪膠合板和柔軟低噪音布料製成的4乘4地毯隔音間」演出。在瓊斯的建議下，-{zh-cn:她;zh-hk:她;zh-tw:她;}-和瓦昆·菲尼克斯在拍攝過程中避免見面<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vulture.com/2013/10/spike-jonze-on-making-her.html|title=Exclusive:Him and Her: How Spike Jonze Made the Weirdest, Most Timely Romance of the Year|last=Harris|first=Mark|work=New York|date=2013-10-06|access-date=2014-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140228003537/http://www.vulture.com/2013/10/spike-jonze-on-making-her.html|archive-date=2014-02-28|dead-url=no}}</ref>。莫頓之後被換成[[史嘉蕾·喬韓森|史嘉蕾·喬韓森]]。瓊斯解釋道：「這只有在後期制作中，當我們開始剪輯時，我們意識到角色/電影所需要的以及薩曼莎和我共同創造的有所不同。所以我們更換演員，至此以後，-{zh-cn:斯嘉丽;zh-tw:史嘉蕾;zh-hk:施嘉莉;}-便接替了角色。」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vulture.com/2013/06/spike-jonze-replaced-samantha-morton-with-scarjo.html|title=Exclusive: Scarlett Johansson Replaced Samantha Morton in Spike Jonze’s New Film, Her|last=Buchanan|first=Kyle|work=New York|date=2013-06-21|access-date=2019-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140102014900/http://www.vulture.com/2013/06/spike-jonze-replaced-samantha-morton-with-scarjo.html|archive-date=2014-01-02|dead-url=no}}</ref>瓊斯于2013年春季會見史嘉蕾，並與-{zh-cn:她;zh-hk:她;zh-tw:她;}-合作了四個月<ref name="variety1"/><ref name="vulture"/>。在更換演員之後，新的幾幕於2013年8月進行拍攝，這些都是「新想像的」或是「瓊斯最初想拍的但沒有」<ref name="vulture"/>。

===後期製作===
{{link-en|埃里克·桑布魯寧|Eric Zumbrunnen}}和傑夫·布坎南（{{lang|en|Jeff Buchanan}}）是電影的剪輯師。桑布魯寧表示西奧多去相親之後和莎曼珊之間的一幕有「重寫」。他解釋説在那一幕中他們的目標是明確表示「（莎曼珊）正在與（西奧多）產生共鳴並同情他。你會希望感覺到他們之間的關係因這場對話而更親近」<ref>{{cite news|last1=Giardina|first1=Caroline|title=ACE Preview: Editors on Shaping Some of the Year's Biggest Performances|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/behind-screen/ace-preview-editors-shaping-some-676653|accessdate=2015-02-13|work=[[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2014-02-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326091025/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/behind-screen/ace-preview-editors-shaping-some-676653|archive-date=2015-03-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[史蒂文·索德伯格|-{zh-cn:史蒂文·索德伯格; zh-tw:史蒂芬·索德柏; zh-hk:史提芬·蘇德堡;}-]]當瓊斯首剪版本超過150分鐘時參與這部電影，而-{zh-cn:索德伯格; zh-tw:索德柏; zh-hk:蘇德堡;}-剪至90分鐘。這不是電影的最後版本，但它協助瓊斯剪去不需要的次要情節。因此，[[克里斯·庫柏|-{zh-tw:克里斯·庫柏; zh-hk:基斯·谷巴; zh-cn:克里斯·库珀;}-]]所飾演電影中紀錄片主題中的配角在最後剪輯版本遭到刪除<ref name="vulture" />。

當中有幾幕包含了虛構電子遊戲，這一系列均由動畫家{{le|大衛·歐萊禮|David OReilly}}開發。歐萊禮在電影的作品啓發他開發屬於自己的電子遊戲，之後便打造了第一款遊戲《{{le|大山模擬|Mountain (video game)}}》<ref name="atlantic">{{cite web | url = https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2014/07/you-are-mountain/374543/ | title = You Are Mountain | first = Ian | last = Bogost | date = 2014-07-17 | accessdate = 2017-04-03 | work = [[大西洋_(雜誌)|The Atlantic]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170518111243/https://www.theatlantic.com/entertainment/archive/2014/07/you-are-mountain/374543/ | archive-date = 2017-05-18 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 音樂 ===
電影的配樂由[[拱廊之火|拱廊之火]]和{{le|歐文·帕萊特|Owen Pallett}}創作，而帕萊特和拱廊之火的{{le|威廉·巴特勒|William Butler (musician)}}為主要貢獻者<ref name=Behindthescenes>{{cite web|last=Battan|first=Carrie|title=Watch: Arcade Fire and Owen Pallett's Her Score, Behind the Scenes|url=http://pitchfork.com/news/54060-watch-arcade-fire-and-owen-palletts-her-score-behind-the-scenes|website=Pitchfork|date=2014-02-20|accessdate=2015-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151003022021/http://pitchfork.com/news/54060-watch-arcade-fire-and-owen-palletts-her-score-behind-the-scenes/|archive-date=2015-10-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。配樂在[[第86屆奧斯卡金像獎|第86屆奧斯卡金像獎]]獲得[[奥斯卡最佳原创音乐奖|最佳原創音樂]]<ref name=Oscarwin>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-winners-2014-full-list-results-86th-academy-awards-kodak-theater-684748|title=Oscars 2014 Winners: The Complete List|work=The Hollywood Reporter|date=2014-03-02|accessdate=2014-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140723201401/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-winners-2014-full-list-results-86th-academy-awards-kodak-theater-684748|archive-date=2014-07-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除了配樂之外，拱廊之火還為電影創作歌曲《Supersymmetry》，其同樣收錄自他們的專輯《{{le|反射 (專輯)|Reflektor|反射}}》。同專輯中歌曲《Porno》的旋律也可在原聲帶聽到<ref name=Reflektor>{{cite web|last=Eggertsen|first=Chris|title='Her' Q&A: Spike Jonze on why he replaced Samantha Morton with Scarlett Johansson|url=http://www.hitfix.com/in-contention/her-qa-spike-jonze-on-why-he-replaced-samantha-morton-with-scarlett-johansson|website=Hitflix|accessdate=2015-09-18|date=2013-01-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924082323/http://www.hitfix.com/in-contention/her-qa-spike-jonze-on-why-he-replaced-samantha-morton-with-scarlett-johansson|archive-date=2015-09-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[Yeah_yeah_yeahs|耶耶耶合唱團]]主唱{{le|凱倫·O|Karen O}}和[[吸血鬼週末|吸血鬼週末]]主唱{{le|以斯拉·克尼|Ezra Koenig}}共同演唱的歌曲《{{le|The Moon Song|The Moon Song}}》獲得[[奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲奖|奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲]]提名<ref>{{cite web |last=Muller |first=Marissa G. |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/karen-o-and-ezra-koenig-team-for-dreamy-moon-song-song-premiere-20140210 |title=Karen O and Ezra Koenig Team for Dreamy 'Moon Song' – Song Premiere |work=Rolling Stone |date=2014-02-10 |accessdate=2018-02-08 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6O2ovFqgD?url=http://www.rollingstone.com/music/news/karen-o-and-ezra-koenig-team-for-dreamy-moon-song-song-premiere-20140210 |archive-date=2014-03-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

原聲帶無論實體還是數位都沒有發行，而華納兄弟並沒宣佈未來任何發行計劃<ref name="ew">{{cite web|last=Anderson|first=Kyle|title=Want to buy the Oscar-nominated music from the 'Her' soundtrack? You can't|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2014/01/23/her-soundtrack-score-arcade-fire-oscars|work=Entertainment Weekly|accessdate=2015-04-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150509051724/http://www.ew.com/article/2014/01/23/her-soundtrack-score-arcade-fire-oscars|archive-date=2015-05-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年1月，網上有13首的配樂供人串流，但之後遭到下架<ref name="ew"/><ref name="indiewire">{{cite web |last=Jagernauth |first=Kevin |url=http://www.indiewire.com/2014/01/listen-arcade-fires-complete-score-for-spike-jonzes-her-89952/ |title=Listen: Arcade Fire's Complete Score For Spike Jonze's 'Her' |website=IndieWire |date=2014-01-21 |accessdate=2018-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180209003412/http://www.indiewire.com/2014/01/listen-arcade-fires-complete-score-for-spike-jonzes-her-89952/ |archive-date=2018-02-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2016年6月17日，威廉·巴特勒在[[Reddit|Reddit]]的「Ask Me Anything」（AMA）中提及未來發行黑膠唱片的可能性<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.reddit.com/r/indieheads/comments/4okhx2/im_will_butler_ama/d4dc9sd/|title=I'm Will Butler, AMA!|website=[[Reddit|Reddit]]|date=2016-06-17|accessdate=2017-09-27}}</ref>。

