[[File:Her_Premiere_NYFF_2013.jpg|thumb]]、[[史派克·瓊斯|史派克·瓊斯]]、[[艾美·亞當斯|艾美·亞當斯]]、[[魯妮·瑪拉|魯妮·瑪拉]]和[[奧利維亞·魏爾德|奧利維亞·魏爾德]]出席《雲端情人》在2013年[[紐約影展|紐約影展]]的首映會]]
2013年10月12日，《雲端情人》被選為2013年[[紐約影展|紐約影展]]的閉幕片，同時成為它的全球首映<ref>{{cite news|last1=Li|first1=Shirley|title=On the scene with Spike Jonze, Joaquin Phoenix, Rooney Mara, and more at the premiere of 'Her'|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2013/10/13/spike-jonze-her-nyff-premiere|accessdate=2015-02-08|work=[[娛樂周刊|Entertainment Weekly]]|date=2013-10-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150213185101/http://www.ew.com/article/2013/10/13/spike-jonze-her-nyff-premiere|archive-date=2015-02-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。翌日，它在{{le|漢普頓國際影展|Hamptons International Film Festival}}<ref>{{cite web|title=HIFF2013: Day 4 Highlights|url=http://hamptonsfilmfest.org/features/hiff2013-day-4-sunday/|publisher=Hamptons International Film Festival|accessdate=2015-02-13|date=2013-10-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150213185239/http://hamptonsfilmfest.org/features/hiff2013-day-4-sunday/|archive-date=2015-02-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。該片還參與第8屆[[罗马电影节|羅馬影展]]競賽，而喬韓森贏得最佳女演員<ref>{{cite news|last1=Barnes|first1=Henry|title=Scarlett Johansson voted best actress for voice-only role in Her|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/nov/18/scarlett-johansson-her-best-actress|accessdate=2015-02-13|work=[[衛報|The Guardian]]|date=2013-11-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141007170851/http://www.theguardian.com/film/2013/nov/18/scarlett-johansson-her-best-actress|archive-date=2014-10-07|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影於2013年11月20日透過[[華納兄弟|華納兄弟影業]]在北美有限上映<ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2013/film/news/joaquin-phoenixs-her-dated-for-nov-20-by-warner-bros-1200486032|title=Warner Bros. Sets Joaquin Phoenix Pic 'Her' for Nov. 20|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|date=2013-05-21|accessdate=2013-05-22|last=McNary|first=Dave|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130617173831/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/joaquin-phoenixs-her-dated-for-nov-20-by-warner-bros-1200486032/|archive-date=2013-06-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它後來推遲至2013年12月18日有限上映，而為順應獎季活動，該片於2014年1月10日廣泛上映<ref>{{cite web |url=https://variety.com/2013/film/news/joaquin-phoenixs-her-pushed-back-for-awards-campaign-1200577737/ |title=Joaquin Phoenix's 'Her' Pushed Back for Awards Campaign |work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]] |date=2013-08-13 |accessdate=2013-08-19 |last=McNary |first=Dave |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130815205042/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/joaquin-phoenixs-her-pushed-back-for-awards-campaign-1200577737/ |archive-date=2013-08-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年5月13日，《雲端情人》由{{le|華納家庭娛樂|Warner Home Video}}以[[藍光光碟|藍光光碟]]和[[DVD|DVD]]形式發行。藍光光碟包含三段幕後花絮，而DVD則包含一段花絮<ref>{{cite web|last1=Gallagher|first1=Brian|title='Her' Blu-ray and DVD Arrive May 13th|url=http://www.movieweb.com/her-blu-ray-and-dvd-arrive-may-13th|publisher=MovieWeb|accessdate=2015-01-18|date=2014-03-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150119180739/http://www.movieweb.com/her-blu-ray-and-dvd-arrive-may-13th|archive-date=2015-01-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影的DVD和藍光光碟銷售額分別爲220萬美元和270萬美元，家用媒體的總額爲490萬美元<ref>{{cite web|title=Her|url=http://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Her#tab=summary|publisher=The Numbers|accessdate=2015-01-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150108185227/http://www.the-numbers.com/movie/Her#tab=summary|archive-date=2015-01-08|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===評價===
[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]收集的266篇專業影評文章中，「新鮮度」為94%，平均得分8.5分（滿分10分）。網站的共識評價爲「甜美、深情和聰明。史派克·瓊斯的《雲端情人》利用其稍偏科幻的劇情，來傳達出關於現代人際關係現狀那詼諧有趣的智慧」<ref name="Rotten Tomatoes">{{cite web | url= http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/her/ | title= Her (2013) | publisher= [[爛番茄|Rotten Tomatoes]] | accessdate= 2019-04-09 | archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160531151211/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/her | archive-date= 2016-05-31 | dead-url= no }}</ref>，而基於另一影評網站[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]基於47篇評論文章，平均分爲90（滿分100），代表「普遍好評」<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.metacritic.com/movie/her |title= Her |publisher= [[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |accessdate= 2018-05-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20140819015510/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/her |archive-date= 2014-08-19 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。據[[影院评分|CinemaScore]]進行的調查，觀眾的平均評價於A+至F間落於「B-」<ref name="CinemaScore">{{cite web |url=https://m.cinemascore.com |title=Her - CinemaScore |work=[[影院评分|CinemaScore]].com |access-date=2019-04-24 |archive-url=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20170916153548/https://m.cinemascore.com/ |archive-date=2017-09-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《[[滾石_(雜誌)|滾石]]》的[[彼得·崔維斯|彼得·崔維斯]]給予電影3.5顆星（滿分4顆），尤其讚賞喬韓森的演出，稱-{zh-cn:她;zh-hk:她;zh-tw:她;}-「聲演莎曼珊擁有甜美、性感、關懷、控制欲和恐怖的腔調」以及-{zh-cn:她;zh-hk:她;zh-tw:她;}-的「聲音傑作值得獲獎」。他還接著稱瓊斯「一個有遠見的人」<ref>{{cite web |last=Travers |first=Peter |url=https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/her-20131218 |title='Her' Movie Review |newspaper=[[滾石_(雜誌)|Rolling Stone]] |date=2013-12-18 |accessdate=2014-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170929001025/https://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/her-20131218 |archive-date=2017-09-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[時代雜誌|時代]]》的{{le|理查德·科利斯|Richard Corliss}}稱讚菲尼克斯的演出，並將他的角色與《[[地心引力_(电影)|-{zh-cn:地心引力;zh-hk:引力邊緣;zh-tw:地心引力;}-]]》的[[珊卓·布拉克|珊卓·布拉克]]和《[[一切尽失|-{zh-hk:怒海求生; zh-tw:海上求生記; zh-cn:一切尽失;}-]]》的[[勞勃·瑞福|勞勃·瑞福]]作比較：「菲尼克斯必須親自傳達他電影中實際上的意義和感受。而他做到了，並帶著微妙的優雅和深度。（……）菲尼克斯向我們展示了當一顆哀悼之心活躍起來的樣子——因為他深愛著《雲端情人》。」科利斯引用[[HAL_9000|HAL 9000]]和《[[虛擬偶像|虛擬偶像]]》為《雲端情人》的電影前身並讚賞喬韓森，稱-{zh-cn:她;zh-hk:她;zh-tw:她;}-的演出「具有魅力和迷人」<ref name="TIME">{{cite web |last=Corliss |first=Richard |url=http://entertainment.time.com/2013/10/12/spike-jonzes-her-falling-in-love-with-the-it-girl/ |title=Spike Jonze's 'her': Falling in Love With the IT Girl |work=[[時代雜誌|Time]] |date=2013-10-12 |accessdate=2014-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170309042627/http://entertainment.time.com/2013/10/12/spike-jonzes-her-falling-in-love-with-the-it-girl/ |archive-date=2017-03-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[好萊塢報導|好萊塢報導]]》的[[陶德·麥卡錫|陶德·麥卡錫]]雖然對於結局比其他電影更為普通表達出失望，但稱其為「一個非常高階的探索性和鑽研性的作品」。麥卡錫審查了故事的前提，而間接表明這部電影的主要虛擬戀情比[[瑞恩·高斯林|-{zh-hk:賴恩·高斯寧;zh-tw:雷恩·葛斯林;zh-cn:瑞恩·高斯林;}-]]在《[[充氣娃娃之戀|充氣娃娃之戀]]》的角色與性愛娃娃的感情更好。麥卡錫將菲尼克斯「溫柔」和「易碎」的演出與他在《[[大师_(电影)|-{zh-hk:大師;zh-cn:大师;zh-tw:世紀教主;}-]]》「嚇人」的演出作比較。他還讚賞瓊斯的創作，因為它洞察了人對於愛和關係的渴望，以及當中的演技「（讓）它全部感覺變得自發性和堅定」<ref>{{cite news |last=McCarthy |first=Todd |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/her/review/648073 |title=Her: Film Review |work=[[好萊塢報導|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=2013-10-12 |accessdate=2014-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140511185804/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/movie/her/review/648073 |archive-date=2014-05-11 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

{{tsl|en|Richard Roeper|理查·洛普}}説這部電影是「年度最原創、最好笑，甚至最令人心碎的故事之一」，以及稱菲尼克斯「完美出演」<ref>{{cite web|last1=Roeper|first1=Richard|title=Her|url=http://www.richardroeper.com/reviews/her.aspx|publisher=RichardRoeper.com|accessdate=2015-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150216010029/http://www.richardroeper.com/reviews/her.aspx|archive-date=2015-02-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[紐約時報|紐約時報]]》的曼諾拉·達吉斯（{{lang|en|Manohla Dargis}}）將它命名為「同時是一個出色概念上的玩笑和一出深度真誠的浪漫劇」<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/18/movies/her-directed-by-spike-jonze.html |title=Disembodied, but, Oh, What a Voice |last=Dargis |first=Manohla |publisher=The New York Times |date=2013-12-17 |accessdate=2015-03-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150422055341/http://www.nytimes.com/2013/12/18/movies/her-directed-by-spike-jonze.html |archive-date=2015-04-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[今日美國|今日美國]]》的克勞蒂亞·普伊格（{{lang|en|Claudia Puig}}）分別稱菲尼克斯和喬韓森的演出為「出衆」和「完美程度」。-{zh-cn:她;zh-hk:她;zh-tw:她;}-進一步稱讚這部電影具有「創意性、親密性和諷刺的詼諧性」<ref>{{cite news|last1=Puig|first1=Claudia|title=Joaquin Phoenix makes a connection with 'Her'|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2013/12/18/her-review/3552853/|accessdate=2015-02-13|work=[[今日美國|USA Today]]|date=2013-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221084141/http://www.usatoday.com/story/life/movies/2013/12/18/her-review/3552853/|archive-date=2015-02-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[福布斯|-{zh-cn:福布斯;zh-sg:资本家杂志;zh-hk:福布斯;zh-tw:富比士;}-]]》的斯科特·孟德爾森（{{lang|en|Scott Mendelson}}）稱《雲端情人》是「電影中具有創造性和令人產生共鳴的瑰寶」，讚賞喬韓森「絕妙的聲音演出」以及魯妮·瑪拉、奧利維亞·魏爾德和艾美·亞當斯的配角演出<ref>{{cite news|last1=Mendelson|first1=Scott|title=Review: 'Her' Is Inventive, Thoughtful, And Humane|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2013/12/11/review-her-is-inventive-thoughtful-and-humane/|accessdate=2015-02-13|work=[[福布斯|Forbes]]|date=2013-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150330222453/http://www.forbes.com/sites/scottmendelson/2013/12/11/review-her-is-inventive-thoughtful-and-humane/|archive-date=2015-03-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《[[環球郵報|環球郵報]]》的連恩·拉西（{{lang|en|Liam Lacey}}）説這部電影「溫柔又怪異」，讚賞它的幽默，並認為它比瓊斯的《[[傀儡人生|-{zh-hans:成为约翰马尔科维奇;zh-hk:玩謝麥高維治;zh-tw:變腦;}-]]》和《[[兰花窃贼|-{zh-cn:改编剧本;zh-hk:何必偏偏玩謝我;zh-tw:蘭花賊;}-]]》更像[[查理·卡夫曼|-{zh-cn:查理·考夫曼;zh-hk:查理·卡夫曼;zh-tw:查理·考夫曼;}-]]的《{{link-en|紐約浮世繪|Synecdoche, New York|-{zh-hans:纽约提喻法; zh-tw:紐約浮世繪;}-}}》。然而，拉西還表示菲尼克斯的演出是「真正的脆弱」，以及「他的情感抑制發展還開始壓倒了整部電影」<ref>{{cite news|last1=Lacey|first1=Liam|title=Her: Spike Jonze delivers a gentle and eccentric lonely-guy movie|url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/life/holiday-guide/holiday-survival-guide/her-spike-jonze-delivers-a-gentle-and-eccentric-lonely-guy-movie/article16003228/|accessdate=2015-02-13|work=[[環球郵報|The Globe and Mail]]|date=2014-12-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150714063619/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/life/holiday-guide/holiday-survival-guide/her-spike-jonze-delivers-a-gentle-and-eccentric-lonely-guy-movie/article16003228/|archive-date=2015-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

相反，《[[舊金山紀事報|舊金山紀事報]]》的{{link-en|米克·拉塞爾|Mick LaSalle}}批評故事、節奏和菲尼克斯的角色。他還認為這部電影是「想比看有趣許多」<ref>{{cite news|last1=LaSalle|first1=Mick|title='Her' review: No future in virtual relationship|url=http://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/Her-review-No-future-in-virtual-relationship-5091276.php|accessdate=2015-01-22|work=San Francisco Chronicle|date=2013-12-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150122160731/http://www.sfgate.com/movies/article/Her-review-No-future-in-virtual-relationship-5091276.php|archive-date=2015-01-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《{{le|芝加哥讀者報|Chicago Reader}}》的J·R·瓊斯（{{lang|en|J. R. Jones}}）給予電影2顆星（滿分4顆），讚賞菲尼克斯和喬韓森的演出，但批評菲尼克斯的角色，稱他是「白癡」。他還批評菲尼克斯和喬韓森角色的關係少了現實性<ref>{{cite news|last1=Jones|first1=J. R.|title=This Is Between Me and ''Her'' (And Spike Jonze)|url=http://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/her-spike-jonze-joaquin-phoenix-scarlett-johansson/Content?oid=12360147|accessdate=2015-01-22|work=Chicago Reader|date=2014-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150122160638/http://www.chicagoreader.com/chicago/her-spike-jonze-joaquin-phoenix-scarlett-johansson/Content?oid=12360147|archive-date=2015-01-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《{{le|村聲|The Village Voice}}》的{{le|史蒂芬妮·扎哈瑞克|Stephanie Zacharek}}認為瓊斯是「太着迷於他那處於中心的自負所以無法超越它」，並批評對白是「有預謀」。然而，-{zh-cn:她;zh-hk:她;zh-tw:她;}-稱讚喬韓森的演出，稱它是「電影的可取之處」，並認為《雲端情人》「沒有喬韓森不僅僅是無法想像——它沒有-{zh-cn:她;zh-hk:她;zh-tw:她;}-實在令人無法忍受」<ref>{{cite news|last1=Zacharek|first1=Stephanie|title=''Her'': iLove, American Style|url=http://www.villagevoice.com/2013-12-18/film/her-movie-review/|accessdate=2015-01-22|work=The Village Voice|date=2013-12-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141231154538/http://www.villagevoice.com/2013-12-18/film/her-movie-review/|archive-date=2014-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2022年5月，本片在Metacritic影史百大科幻電影排名中得到第10名<ref>{{cite web|title=Top Sci-Fi Movies|url=https://www.metacritic.com/browse/movies/genre/metascore/sci-fi?view=condensed|accessdate=2022-05-14|author=|date=|format=|publisher=|language=en|website=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]|archive-date=2022-05-14|archive-url=https://www.metacritic.com/browse/movies/genre/metascore/sci-fi?view=condensed|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===票房===
截止至首週週末，《雲端情人》在6家影院共收獲258,000美元票房，平均每影院收獲43,000美元<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3765&p=.htm |title=Weekend Report: Burgundy Beaten by Bilbo |publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |date=2013-12-22 |accessdate=2014-05-19 |quote=...earned a solid $258,000 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224110612/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3765&p=.htm |archive-date=2013-12-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。電影於2014年1月10日擴展至1,729家影院廣泛上映之前，就在有限上映時收獲超過300萬美金票房<ref>{{cite web |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3770&p=.htm |title=Forecast: 'Lone Survivor' to Outlast 'Hercules' this Weekend |publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |date=2014-01-09 |accessdate=2014-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140501062359/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3770&p=.htm |archive-date=2014-05-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。截止至廣泛上映的首週週末，電影共收獲530萬美元票房<ref name="mojo3771">{{cite web|last=Subers |first=Ray |url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3771&p=.htm |title=Weekend Report: Audiences Flock to 'Lone Survivor,' Avoid 'Hercules,' 'Her' |publisher=[[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |date=2014-01-12 |accessdate=2014-08-04 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6RZl1DyHV?url=http://boxofficemojo.com/news/?id=3771 |archivedate=2014-08-04 |deadurl=no |df= }}</ref>。《雲端情人》在美國及加拿大地區共累積了2,560萬美元的票房，加上來自其他地區的2,180萬美元，全球票房共計4,740萬美元<ref name="mojo">{{cite web |title= Her (2013) |url= http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=her2013.htm |work= [[Box_Office_Mojo|Box Office Mojo]] |publisher= [[Internet_Movie_Database|Internet Movie Database]] |accessdate= 2015-07-11 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20130621201608/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=her2013.htm |archive-date= 2013-06-21 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

===榮譽===
{{Main|《她》获奖名单}}
《雲端情人》獲得許多獎項和提名，尤其是瓊斯的劇本。電影在[[第86屆奥斯卡金像奖|第86屆奥斯卡金像奖]]獲得五項提名，當中包括[[奥斯卡最佳影片奖|最佳影片]]，而瓊斯贏得[[奧斯卡最佳原創劇本獎|最佳原創劇本]]<ref>{{cite web|title=2014 Oscar Nominees|publisher=[[电影艺术与科学学院|Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences]]|url=http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/86/nominees.html|accessdate=2014-01-16|date=2014-01-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006093645/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/86/nominees.html|archive-date=2014-10-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-winners-2014-full-list-results-86th-academy-awards-kodak-theater-684748|title=Oscars 2014 Winners: The Complete List|work=[[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]]|date=2014-03-02|accessdate=2014-03-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140723201401/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/oscar-winners-2014-full-list-results-86th-academy-awards-kodak-theater-684748|archive-date=2014-07-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它在[[第71屆金球獎|第71屆金球獎]]獲得三項提名，而瓊斯贏得[[金球獎最佳劇本|最佳劇本]]<ref name="Golden Globe Awards Winners">{{cite news|url=https://variety.com/2014/film/news/golden-globe-awards-winners-2014-list-golden-globes-1201050486/|title=Golden Globe Awards Winners|work=[[綜藝_(雜誌)|Variety]]|date=2014-01-12|accessdate=2014-03-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140320084120/http://variety.com/2014/film/news/golden-globe-awards-winners-2014-list-golden-globes-1201050486/|archive-date=2014-03-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。瓊斯還贏得[[美國編劇工會獎|美國編劇工會獎]]和[[廣播影評人協會獎|廣播影評人協會獎]]<ref name="Golden Globe Awards Winners"/><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/2014-critics-choice-awards-winners-671707|title=Critics' Choice Awards: The Winners|work=[[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]]|accessdate=2015-02-13|date=2014-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141017063852/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/2014-critics-choice-awards-winners-671707|archive-date=2014-10-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在{{link-en|第40屆土星獎|40th Saturn Awards}}，電影贏得[[土星獎最佳奇幻電影|最佳奇幻電影]]、喬韓森贏得[[土星獎最佳電影女配角|最佳電影女配角]]以及瓊斯贏得{{link-en|土星獎最佳劇本|Saturn Award for Best Writing|最佳劇本}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hitfix.com/in-contention/2014-saturn-awards-winners|title='Gravity,' 'Iron Man 3,' 'Breaking Bad' and 'The Walking Dead' lead 2014 Saturn Award winners|publisher=[[HitFix|HitFix]]|date=2014-06-27|accessdate=2015-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140630234600/http://www.hitfix.com/in-contention/2014-saturn-awards-winners|archive-date=2014-06-30|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《雲端情人》還在[[國家評論協會|國家評論協會獎]]贏得[[國家評論協會獎最佳影片|最佳影片]]和{{link-en|國家評論協會獎最佳導演|National Board of Review Award for Best Director|最佳導演}}<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/national-board-review-awards-announced-661763|title='Her' Named Best Film by National Board of Review|work=[[荷里活報道|The Hollywood Reporter]]|publisher=Prometheus Global Media|date=2013-12-04|accessdate=2014-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140227213055/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/national-board-review-awards-announced-661763|archive-date=2014-02-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[美國電影學會|美國電影學會]]將電影排進它的2013年十强電影<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/afi-awards-2013-film-winners-full-list/|title=AFI Awards 2013: Top 10 Films List Is Good News For Major Studios|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline Hollywood]]|date=2014-12-09|accessdate=2014-04-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140424131719/http://www.deadline.com/2013/12/afi-awards-2013-film-winners-full-list/|archive-date=2014-04-24|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

